zepiratesOfTheCaribbeaniv_v6_1

SORRY THAT IT TOOK SO LONG TO FIX THIS!!! :(

Map By TaskuVaras, design Taskuvaras and sotamies[fin](Cimbe)
fixed: zm round deleted, humans dont die at the end,hold spotc made more challenging, levels made harder, bugs fixed
info: map is based on PIRATES OF THE CARIBBEAN ON STRANGER TIDES map goes all the way from white cab bay to the fountain of youth passing ponce de leon and other places from that great movie.
map includes: - super weapons on some levels - 4 levels (easy, normal, hard, extreme) - custom music, particles and models - multiple paths - dev room - hdr and cubemaps
I hope you like the map. Feel free to ask if you have any questions, I will be happy to answer them. And of course I would like to hear your feedback. But please spend some time testing the map and writing your feedback and remember, as constructive as possible.
you are not allowed decompile or make any changes to this map
